text_content:
Awesome intelligent and handsome little big guy !  He is so very blessed to have been rescued and brought to your facility. And I absolutely love that he has a fan club 🙂 What a lucky little fellow to have so many people to love him. I certainly fell in love with him right away the first time I saw him in this video. Thank all of you for your kindness and love you give to him and all of your rescues. What a great way to start my day learning about Otis for the first time.
         Sincerely; 
                ~Charles H. Farish~

@sg_animals hi i have just discovered your channel whilst searching for Musk Turtle care. I watched part 2 first and now part 1. Both videos are very informative and very well done. Thank you for making these videos  that are so helpful for us newbies keeping Musk Turtles. I have 2 babies and love them both.
Just want to make sure I am giving them everything they need to grow strong and stay healthy.
Hope you are well and Marie too, she is lovely ❤❤❤
